</p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ufizzlebeemhb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fizzlebee MHB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(12/21/00 4:12:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/enkulka?flezbwidth=100&flezbheight=300?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Has this  happened to anyone else?</span><hr size=1> I have never had this happen to me, and if it did the wizzie would get a good talking to on Magician Tactics.<br>
<br>
In a normal group (1-2 tanks, me and whoever else decides to show) I will DS the puller, DS the next person who gets hit the most (takes a few pulls to realize who this is) send in my fire pet, tell the tanks to NOT taunt. and then blast it once with SoS when I think its enough to kill the mob.  This takes me a total of 1 bubble.  The tanks lose about a bubble of health and my pet is usually at 60-70%<br>
